snippet.title: Gully | New Movie Trailer 2021 | Drama/Crime
snippet.description:
Three friends from a rough Los Angeles neighborhood embark on a wild night of out-of-control partying. But when the rampage stops, the retribution begins.

Initial release: 4 June 2021 (USA)
Director: Nabil Elderkin

Cast:
Amber Heard (Joyce)
Charlie Plummer (Nicky)
Jacob Latimore (Calvin)
Jonathan Majors (Greg)
